caption.text:
Game of the day, Internationalsoccer for the Atari 2600.  Released in 1982 by M Network(Mattel Electronics), it is for 2 players and follows soccer rules.  Each player has to score more goals then the other in two 45 minute periods(simulated time). Each player controls one player in the field at a time while the computer controls the rest.  The player can dribble and pass, and features throw ins, corner kicks, goal kicks, and over time in the event of a tie.  There are also several.skill levels which affect the speed of the game.
.
.
.
.
.

✨💍 Sol Ring
Let's kick off #MasterpieceMonday with this ✨Shiny Boi. Four years ago when I started my adventure into magic with my first M15 core deck builders tool kit I remember thinking I would never spend another $20 on magic again. Then later that Christmas my cousin got me my first ever Commander deck Yidris, Maelstrom Wielder and I've been hooked ever since. So I grew my collection slowly over time since then and I ended up with 20+ commander decks. With not enough time to play them, I decided it was time to trade in some of my decks and get some cards I've been infatuated with since I started playing commander. And win or lose the satisfaction of playing such a beautiful card gives me satisfaction. That being said Im still competitive and my new deck is still a work in progress. But... I can't wait to share it with all of you. Thank you all for looking at this Cardboard art with me ♥️
.

🔷 تأیید انتشار بازی Arise: A Simple Story برای اکس‌باکس وان و رایانه‌های شخصی.

طبق اعلام رسمی شرکت تک‌لند (Techland)، بازی Arise: A Simple Story علاوه بر  پلی‌استیشن ۴، برروی کنسول اکس‌باکس وان و پلتفرم رایانه‌های شخصی نیز منتشر خواهد شد.

بازی Arise: A Simple Story ابتدا در رویداد State of Play 2019 به صورت رسمی برای کنسول پلی‌استیشن ۴ معرفی گردید. این بازی قرار است یک عنوان به شدت احساسی و منحصر به فرد باشد که به نظر می‌رسد از سبک هنری عنوان دوست‌داشتنی Journey الهام گرفته است. توسعه‌دهندگان این بازی در نظر دارند تا رویاهای انسان‌ها را در قالب بازی ویدئویی، به واقعیت تبدیل کنند و احساسات مختلفی از جمله شادی و ناراحتی را به بازی‌بازان منتقل نمایند. همچنین بازی‌بازان می‌توانند این بازی را به صورت تک‌نفره و یا دونفره تجربه کنند.

بازی Arise: A Simple Story  در تاریخ سه‌شنبه، ۱۲ آذرماه ۱۳۹۸ (۳ دسامبر) برای کنسول‌های پلی‌استیشن ۴، اکس‌باکس وان و پلتفرم رایانه‌های شخصی منتشر خواهد شد. ➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖➖

Hi Gamers,
Let’s head back, just a little bit..Okay to be honest, 11 years ago, to 2008.

In October 2008, Ubisoft released Far Cry 2. An open world first-person shooter, that takes place in a modern-day Central African nation during civil war. You, the player,takes control of a mercenary on a lengthy journey to locate and assassinate "The Jackal", a notorious arms dealer.

The game was met with positive reception upon release with critics praising the game's open-ended gameplay, the AI, the settings and the visuals of the game. Some reports state that the game was ahead of it’s time.

Some interesting facts about the game, is that you as a player, yell in Afrikaans if you are caught in a gunfight, you have to take your Malaria Pills otherwise you will die, you carry syrettes with you to aid yourself if you loose health and when nearing death(when only one health bar remains) you, the player, have to perform first-aid to your character, for example removing bullets with pliers or snapping or twisting broken fingers back into place.

The game has realistic features such as weapon degradation and the dynamic weather system. The player needs to hold a physical map and use a handheld navigation system (which highly resembles a military-type GPS) to get around, but they are automatically updated as the player travels through the environment.

For me, a gamer that never got into the Far Cry Franchise, Far Cry 2 is a definitely must play and just to enjoy a game that has made his mark silently into our hearts. The game is Backwards compataible with Xbox one.
So if you are a Xbox gamer, get it, play it and enjoy it.

Leave a comment about this game or any other game you think is underrated and needs more appreciation.💪🎮 - Gommie😎

caption.text: Bullseye🎯 #ps4#xboxone  #ps4 #gamers #callofduty xbox#ps3#gamers #videogames #gamerguys  #ps4pro#callofdutyblackops4 #gamergirl #gamerforlife#fortnite #gaming#france #usa #blackops4 #bf4 #pubg#instagram  #blackout#gamerlife #ps4gaming #girlgamers #gamingguys#gamergirl#gamerlife#gamergirl#callofduty

.
أكثر الشركات التي تدور حولها الشائعات، Rockstar Games وماهو مشروعهم القادم، هل هو Grand Theft Auto 6 أو Bully 2؟
-
اخر الشائعات التي ظهرت على الإنترنت وبالتحديد موقع Reddit ذكرت بأن Grand Theft Auto 6 هي بالفعل تحت التطوير الكامل منذ ٢٠١٨ تحت الاسم الرمزي Project Americas، كما أشيع مسبقاً.
-
الاستوديو الذي يتولى تطويرها هو Rockstar North، بينما Rockstar India مسؤولون حالياً عن Bully 2 للجيل الحالي والقادم.
-
اللعبة تدور أحداثها في Vice City، والخريطة ستضم مدن ومستنقعات وجزر صغيرة وكبيرة، وستكون أفضل من Grand Theft Auto 5. كما سيكون هناك مهمات محددة في Liberty City
-
أسلوب اللعب سيكون شبيه بالجزء الخامس، لكن هناك اختلافات ستجعله مميز. تدور أحداث اللعبة في عدة فترات زمنية مختلفة واللاعب سيرى التغير الذي سيطرأ على المدينة والمركبات مع التقدم في القصة.
-
الطقس والتقلبات الجوية وتنوعها سيلعب دوراً كبيراً في هذا الجزء، لذلك توقع وجود صواعق، فيضانات، وأعاصير.
-
تماماً كالجزء الخامس، قرارتك واختياراتك هي التي ستحدد نهاية القصة.
-
كل هذي إشاعة، لكن شي جميل ودي يكون حقيقة، انتوا وش رايكم؟ 😍
.
.
.
.
.

Okay so my selfie game may not be strong here so please forgive me 😝 but I feel good today and I wanted to show off my new Mario Kart sweater that I just got. I know I’m going to wear this one into the ground. At the store they only had this one size and when it fit perfectly it’s like it was waiting there all along for me. Most days on my day off I tend to stay at home like a bit of a recluse and try to get a bunch of things done. Today I decided to take myself out for amazing drive with the top down, music playing and I visited one of my favourite beaches out of town that reminds me of my adventures in Hawaii 🌸 . Sometimes you just gotta ignore the chores and endless to-do lists and enjoy life and all the magical moments and take time for yourself. It’s something I have to try to remember. Hope your all having a great day and that you found time to do something for yourself today, if you did what was it? ❤️. It’s okay if it’s even finding time to play your favourite game, that’s what I plan to do later 😝. The sweater gives you a good indication of what I will play.
.
.
.

Machi Koro is all about rolling dice and hoping that whatever you roll gets you money. 
Then, you use that money to buy stuff that gets you money when you roll other numbers. 
Roll, then buy. Roll, then buy. It's like capitalism, only... Yeah, it's like capitalism. 
What’s neat about this game is that you can obtain cards that lets you get money when other players roll that number, so you’re always paying attention to what everyone is doing. 
It's easy to teach, fun to play, and helps people see how fun board games can be.

.
طبق یک اختراع جدید ثبت شده که در فضای مجازی دیده شد، کنسول PlayStation 5 یک هوش مصنوعی نوآورانه خواهد داشت که در بازی‌ها به بازیکنان کمک می‌رساند. .
 این اختراغ جدید که توسط دنیل احمد (تحلیل‌گر معتبر و معروف بازی‌های ویدیویی) دیده شد، برای چیزی به نام PlayStation Assisst است که یک هوش مصنوعی با صداست و در هر بازی به بازیکنان کمک می‌کند. این کمک‌دهنده طبق وضعیت بازیکن در بازی به درخواست‌ها به‌ شکل پویا پاسخ خواهد داد؛ به عنوان مثال، درباره نزدیک‌ترین بسته سلامتی سوال کنید تا بازی آن را روی نقشه برای شما علامت بزند.
.

در حالی که این ویژگی برای بازیکنان حرفه‌ای بخش‌های تک‌نفره و چندنفره چیز خاصی را تغییر نمی‌دهد، اما برای افراد تازه‌وارد و غیر حرفه‌ای که برای تکمیل بازی‌ها به کمک نیاز دارند، امکان بسیار خوبی است

preview_comments.text: How can I be a runner of the month?

caption.text:
September 2019 Runner of the Month - Heffie6!
.
Heffie6 has been playing Temple Run since 2011, and she has also played both Temple Run Brave and Oz. Her son-in-law was the first to play Temple Run in the family and was the one who introduced the game to her. When Heffie6 had an unfortunate stroke, her son-in-law told her that she should check out Temple Run. That it was a fun game to pass the time and it was also a great way to train for her co-ordination. “He was so right,” she says! Imangi is ecstatic that Temple Run had helped Heffie6 through hard times, and is there for her during the best times as well. Once Heffie6 recovered, she also mentioned that she once walked on hot coals to raise money for the local stroke rehab center. “It was an amazing experience!,” she says. It was a confidence booster for her, and she raised over 700euros! Way to go Heffie6!
.
Heffie6 enjoys photography, it’s a hobby of hers. Do you know who else also enjoys photography? No other than the famous Maria Selva! Yup, you’ve guessed it, Maria Selva is Heffie6’s favorite runner. When you can find yourself in one of the runners, you can’t help to latch on to them as your favorite. Can you also relate to one of the runners in Temple Run, just like Heffie6?
.
It was difficult for Heffie6 to choose her favorite map in TR2. It was like trying to choose between your two favorite ice cream flavors, it’s impossible! She’s a big fan of both Lost Jungle and Pirate Cove. Both maps keep her on her toes with so many different obstacles. She says, Pirate Cove feels like there’s more coins to collect, and Lost Jungle has elephants, which is her favorite animal. While running in her favorite maps, she likes setting her own personal goals, outside what the game haves to offer. She likes setting goals to increase her total for coins and gems. Her goal is to reach 20 million coins and 43 thousand gems. Wow!! That’s a crazy amount of loot there! Heffie6 will have to share screenshots with us all once she reaches her goal, if she hasn’t already! With a high score of 21,436,800 (with no save me), there’s no doubt she’ll reach her own personal goals in no time.
If in doubt, flat out!

☆ *🎮🕹🎮🕹🎮🕹* ☆
.
[ÉVÉNEMENT RGB - NUIT DES BIBLIOTHÈQUES 2019]
.
Hello la compagnie
.
🎮 Nous avons le plaisir de vous annoncer que notre association animera un stand Retrogaming lors de l'événement organisé par Bordeaux Métropole : "La nuit des bibliothèques". Nous serons présents le samedi 12 octobre 2019, de 18h à 22h, à la médiathèque de Mérignac.
.
🕹 Pour l'occasion, ce ne sera pas moins de 10 postes de jeux que nous mettrons en place, soit la plus grosse intervention que nous ayons eu à réaliser jusqu'à maintenant.
.
🎮 Un grand merci à Olivier Boisseau du Musée Replay qui a conseillé l'association RGB à la médiathèque de Mérignac, et à Mme Stella DELORD, qui s'est chargée de mettre en place cette intervention.
.
Une fréquentation importante nous y attend, il nous tarde déjà d'y être !
.
ENJOY !!!
.

In the first age, in the first battle, when the shadows first lengthened, one stood. Burned by the embers of Armageddon, his soul blistered by the fires of Hell and tainted beyond ascension, he chose the path of perpetual torment. In his ravenous hatred he found no peace; and with boiling blood he scoured the Umbral Plains seeking vengeance against the dark lords who had wronged him. He wore the crown of the Night Sentinels, and those that tasted the bite of his sword named him... the Doom Slayer.

Tipton HS English teacher and Esports coach & co-founder of the Indiana’s State Esports league is being interviewed by WISH-TV’s Randall Newsome this afternoon in a segment that aired live from THS’ Esports gaming room/virtual reality lab designed and put together by Robertson.
